# Ignore everything in the project root by default
*

# Do not ignore .gitignore and README.md and TCs
!.gitignore
!README.md
!SV95_QA_Style_Full_TCs.md
!.github/
!.github/**
!scripts/
!scripts/**
!fetch_all_tickets.py
!*.md
!*.pdf
!*.docx
!*.xlsx
!*.svg
!*.png
!*.skill

# Do not ignore skills directory and its contents recursively
!skills/
!skills/**

# Ignore system metadata inside allowed directories
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/~$*
